Class Description
DemoDataLoader
Loads 30 demo recipes from demo_recipes file into connected database.

Implementation of Storage Service interface for storing Images locally on application server's filesystem.
FluffyBearApplication
Starting point of the spring boot java backend application for the recipes app develop for mobile application development.
ImageController
Controller Class for handling image requests and saving/returning recipe images.
Ingredient
Class for modelling an ingredient by uid, name and recipes it is contained in.
IngredientController
Controller Class for handling ingredient requests and saving/returning ingredients.
IngredientRepository
Spring boot repository for Ingredients which extends a CrudRepository
IngredientService
Spring boot service for ingredients.
Recipe
Class for modelling an recipe by uid, name, image, cooking time, category (breakfast, lunch, dinner) wether it is vegetarian/vegan, needed ingredients and cooking instructions.
RecipeController
Controller Class for handling recipe requests and saving/filtering/returning recipes as well as related ingredients.
RecipeIngredient
Class for modeling the bidirectional relationship between a recipe and its containing ingredients.
RecipeIngredientRepository
Spring boot repository for RecipeIngredient which extends a CrudRepository
RecipeIngredientService
Spring boot service for ingredients related to recipes.
RecipeRepository
Spring boot repository for Recipes which extends a CrudRepository
RecipeService
Spring boot service for recipes.
StorageErrorCode
Error enum for StorageErrors
StorageService
Interface for a storages service which persists multi part files.
StorageServiceException
Exception for storage service releated errors.
